value.string: On the beach! Great views, beautiful furniture, good vacation rental income, strategically located....what more do you need? Top floor expansive views of the water, West Maui mountains and all the way to Wailuku are visible from the living room, bedroom and lanai. Haleakala and Makena can be seen out the front door. Private lanai. $35,000 of remodeling include tile floors throughout, 2 beautifully tiled showers, and granite countertop in the kitchen. Amenities including solar heated swimming pool, expansive BBQ and beachside shower. You'll enjoy this for years to come...call to see today! A Smoke Free Property.

Nicely upgraded 1 bedroom, 1 bath near the upper pool with a wonderful open kitchen/living room, porcelain tile flooring and newer DeWils cabinetry in kitchen and bath. The bathtub was removed and a walk in shower installed, popcorn ceilings removed and re-textured and on top of all of this, this is the best priced condo in the complex at the time of listing, priced to sell. The complex wide solar water heating system reduces the electric usage. You must see this one before it is gone! Buyers are asked to honor future vacation rental reservations. Seller has the option to qualify this transaction as part of a tax deferred exchange under section 1031 of the Internal Revenue Code.

Ocean view from South facing lanai. Turnkey-vacation rental, offers views of upper pool, expansive lawns & tennis court. Bathroom has been remodeled with designer sliding door into walk-in shower plus lovely granite counter top. Enjoy upscale kitchen which opens to dining and living room area. This is a very spacious one bedroom condo with locked owners closet in bedroom. Also close to Keawakapu Beach with several outstanding beach front restaurants. Wailea shops and dining are 5 minutes away by car. Hale Kamaole features 2 heated swimming pools, tennis court and BBQ's. It's appealing low rise architecture is a frequented, favorite resort in a desired location- directly across the street from white sandy Kamaole Beach III with Kamaole II just north. Perfect location in building 4, 2nd floor and conveniently located in close proximity to elevators and stairs. 2016 is the year to Make Your Dreams Come True. Significant price reduction makes this one an outstanding value.

Ideally located in the South Garden Bldg on the 4th floor. Enchanting ocean views across the expansive heated pool & Jacuzzi area. Fully furnished for vacation rentals. Storage closet in outside walkway for beach gear...Maintenance fee includes electricity, central air conditioning, water, sewer, trash, Cable TV, internet & Long Distance phone service...close to elevator. Sugar Beach Resort is considered a highly desirable vacation choice. Enjoy beautiful sandy beaches and whales returning each winter to calve & mate. Make your dreams come true this year.

Enjoy grand ocean views with swaying palm tree accents from this 4th floor 1 bed 1 bath Kamaole Beach Royale condo. Located just across the street from the white sands and calm waters of south Maui, this lofty vantage point offers spectacular sunsets and whale watching opportunities in the winter. During the warm summer months, you will fully appreciate the new Fujistu A/C system to keep you cool. This prime condo comfortably sleeps 4 and comes fully furnished. Tiled flooring throughout connects to the lanai and brings the outdoors in. Elevator access means no stairs to carry up your beach toys after a fun day in the sun. After a swim in pool, bring your family and friends to the Kamaole Beach Royale’s hidden gem, the rooftop deck with BBQ grills, lounge chairs, tables and amazing 360 views of Maui. Stay into the evening to enjoy stargazing until your hearts content. Monthly HOA fees include cable and electric and typically varies around $350- $400/month with short term rental usage. Currently in rental program with the friendly on-site management. For Drone video please go to: https://youtu.be/Gm2JJbfHOwQ

Rarely available, beach front, ocean view boutique condo on 5 mile, white sand Sugar Beach. Unit has been completely remodeled in July 2015. Kitchen has new quartz counter tops, glass backsplash, and all new stainless appliances. Bathroom is remodeled with Italian Porcelain tile in shower, Hansgrohe Raindance Shower system, 1/2" thick glass shower enclosure and recycled glass mini brick backsplash and wainscoting. Brand new split A/C system, drywall, texture and paint and all new furnishings throughout. This unit is spectacular and must be seen to appreciate all it offers. Only steps to the pool and ocean, yet far enough away to be private. Open House 11/27, 28 and 29th from 1-5 PM.

Wonderful, spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath Hale Kanani condo with an open floor plan. Located across the street from one of Maui’s best beaches, this popular property is not to be missed. Terrific pool, hot tub, and BBQ area. Two parking spaces are included and the property is conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, and activities. Pet friendly complex.

This is the unit you have been waiting for at the extraordinary Kamaole Sands. Located in the prestigious building 3 of the central courtyard. This is a ground floor unit. You will enjoy being able to walk off your lanai to access the pool and spa areas with its convenient location. This is an end unit with only one common wall. Because this is an end unit there is an extra side window in the living room allowing for great sunlight and cross ventilation. You will enjoy the flow of the cooling tropical Maui trade winds. Nicely updated kitchen with granite counter tops. Both bathrooms have also been updated. Unit is in the Castle Rental Program.

Rarely available top floor ocean view unit in building 3! This spectacular 2br/2ba was used as a second home for the last four years. Spacious layout with pantry & closet organizers are a plus. Pet friendly Hale Kanani located just steps away from white sand beaches, shops and restaurants. Two tandem parking stalls, elevator & a central A/C are additional amenities for this lovely complex. Call your realtor today for a private showing. High end furniture negotiable. Mahalo!

One of a kind 2/2 directly on beach in S. Maui. Yes this is a lease hold, but complexes on both sides are twice the price at least. All brand new furniture added to great ocean views, across the street from shops and restaurants with nice ground pool to cool off in. Tile throughout living area, new carpets in both bedrooms. Please Use Vicki, Old Republic has done all work on this.

***This is it if you are looking for a GREAT LOCATION *** Maui Vista has beautifully manicured grounds, outdoor BBQ with entertainment areas, Multiple pools and tennis courts, and it is literally across the street from the famous Charley Young Beach and a very short walk to The Cove surfing spot! There are several popular beaches, local shopping and popular restaurants to dine at, all within walking distance which makes this one of the best places to stay in South Kihei---This Maui Vista 2bd/2ba unit located on the top floor of the desirable building 1 has outstanding ocean views ideal for whale watching or sipping wine while watching the sunset. The open living room and vaulted ceilings gives the unit a feeling of freedom and space! Newly renovated Kitchen boasts, granite counter tops. wine refrigerator and upper end appliances. Stunning slate stair case, leads to privately arranged second floor bedroom with its own bathroom. This fully furnished and decked out vacation rental unit, comes turnkey ready. _______________________________________________Don't Miss The Interactive 3-D Virtual Tour under Video/Virtual Tour button or go to or go to >>> https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=12VjqvZNWpQ&brand=0 <<<

Nicely appointed 4th floor unit located in Building 1, this corner unit has additional windows to let the tropical breeze blow in, and added privacy being an end unit. Watch gorgeous sunsets setting into the ocean, or whales splashing and breaching from the comfort of your lanai. This unit is walking distance to stores, restaurants, local super markets and right across the street from Charley Young beach park. Sold furnished, excluding one art piece and two quilts.

Charming Hawaiian-style decor makes this unit shine! It is located on the shady, north side of the complex so A/C bills are much less. Across the street from Kam 3 for great swimming, snorkeling & shady beaches. Updates include neutral floor tile, painted accent walls, updated kitchen and bathrooms. The open kitchen overlooks a very large living/dining room with some view of the West Maui mountains and sunsets. The complex boasts the largest lanai's in this price range. Each bedroom has a private bath, making it a great vacation rental. This unit not in a rental pool but surrounding units are heavily booked. One assigned covered parking space per unit. Permanent residents may qualify for a tandem parking space. There is a hard-working manager who lives on-site. Don't miss the large enclosed pool area with a shaded gazebo covered by colorful bougainvillea and the covered reading room with small library. Owners can reserve the pool area for private functions. Off-street parking adjacent to the full length of the complex. The association is in then process of installing solar panels to defray the costs of maintaining the common areas. Truly a hidden gem. Some furnishings will be included in the price.

Lowest priced 2/Bed 2/Bath in Kamaole Sands. Ocean view, tiled floors, fully furnished, pool, jacuzzis, beautiful grounds, 4 tennis courts, rental program, and across the street from one of Maui's best beaches.

WONDERFUL OPPORTUNITY to own a beautifully designed, very well priced, top floor unit with fantastic views. Expanded kitchen design with stylish wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless appliances and modern lighting create a tasteful and spacious feeling to the living area, while also greatly increasing the function of the kitchen. Both bathrooms have been well designed with wood cabinets, granite countertops and nice tile work. EXPANSIVE Mountain and Ocean Views from the living/dining/kitchen areas and bedroom. Strong RENTAL HISTORY and INCOME with many repeat guests. Very well maintained unit with ongoing upgrades that clearly demonstrates pride of ownership and a strong commitment to rental guests. This is a MUST SEE!

Watch the beautiful Maui Sunsets from your own perch above it all, on the 6th floor of the Kamaole Beach Royale. The views from this level are breathtaking and the owners installed a mirror on the lanai which makes the view even more exhilarating! A very clean unit with updated kitchen counters and cabinets. This one bedroom, one bath condo sleeps 4 and comes furnished and turn key for you to vacation rent out or simply call it your home in paradise! Did I mention the rooftop view? Not only from your own condo, but you will also be able to enjoy the incredible views from the rooftop deck, complete with Gas BBQ’s, tables, lounge chairs!

Spacious and convenient two bedroom two bath furnished vacation rentable condo. Condo amenities include pool, hot tub, tennis courts, and just a short stroll to popular Kamaole One Beach, restaurants and shopping. Easy to view!

This peaceful and immaculate unit is situated in one of South Maui's most popular vacation rental complexes. Enjoy tennis courts, an expansive pool area with two spas and a wading pool, exercise facilities, outdoor dining areas, and a host of guest services. Conveniently located close to world class shopping & dining in Wailea and Kihei, and across the street from beautiful, family friendly Kamaole Beach Park 3, a local favorite. Recent kitchen upgrades include granite counter tops, a natural stone back splash and stainless steel appliances. Ground floor convenience with access to green space add to the gracious feeling. This unit has a solid rental history and is being offered turn key. Parking stall #143 included. Maintenance fees include: water, trash and internet.

Enjoy HUGE OCEAN VIEWS from this beautiful 2 bedroom DIRECT OCEANFRONT condo! Upgrades include tile floors throughout, fresh paint, newly remodeled showers, beautiful cabinets and countertops. This spacious island top floor condo is clean, move-in ready and being sold fully furnished right down to the linens and dishes. Waipuilani allows 30 day or longer rentals, or you may choose to enjoy this special home as an full time owner/occupant or part time resident. The expansive lawn area that stretches to the water's edge is a great place to enjoy the sunset and there is a nearby public tennis court. Convenient features include the Washer/Dryer located inside the condo, a handy extra storage closet right next to this unit, reserved parking, and a gated Pool/BBQ area. There are only a few other oceanfront 2 bdrm condos in this price range so schedule your showing appointment right away, you won't want to miss this one.

With nice ocean views from the Lanai this 1 bedroom, 2 bath condo is the perfect retreat for you and your renters. New stainless steel alliance in the kitchen and tile throughout the unit make this partial remodeled unit a best buy at Kamaole Sands. 2 air conditioners help cool the entire unit off during those warm days or leave the doors open to bring in a cool breeze for that outdoor living feel. This heavily booked unit will come with future reservations but can make it hard to view so please give your Realtor at least 24 hour notice to guarantee getting in to see the unit.
